Interface Summary
ICancellation Interface of something that can be cancelled, along with cancellation parameters.
IParallelTask<TResult> The interface of a parallel task
IParallelTaskCollection<T,TResult> Interface for grouping tasks for concurrent / background execution
ITaskResult<TResult> Interface of the result created by the work carried out by a task

Enum Summary
TaskResultOrder The order that tasks results are to be returned
 

Exception Summary
TaskCancelledException An exception thrown within a task when the task is cancelled.
TaskResultException Signifies an exception has occurred while running a task.
TaskTimeoutException An exception thrown within a task when the task times out.
